        "data": {
          "Name": "Drogon – Production Forecast (history + prediction, 2018–2025)",
          "Description": "Combined history and prediction production profile for Drogon DG2 Concept Select. History period (Jan 2018 – Jul 2020, 31 months): real OPM Flow simulation output from equinor/fmu-drogon tutorial model (realization-0). 4 producers (A1–A4, phased start Jan–Oct 2018) and 2 water injectors (A5: Jun 2018, A6: Dec 2018). Peak oil rate 14,259 Sm³/d (Oct 2018). Prediction period (Aug 2020 – Jan 2025, 54 months): LRAT-controlled producers (A1/A4: 4,000, A2/A3: 2,500 Sm³/d liquid, BHP limit 150 bar) and water injection (A5/A6: 6,500 Sm³/d each, BHP limit 500 bar). Based on drogon_pred_ref.sch reference case. Cumulative oil at end-of-forecast: 13.9 MSm³ (RF 40.3%). STOIIP = 34.5 MSm³ (simgrid truth case). Water cut rising from 0 to 0.58 (history) to 0.76 (end prediction). Field pressure stabilised at ~255 barsa with voidage replacement.",
          "ColumnBasedTableTypeID": "dev:reference-data--ColumnBasedTableType:AdHoc:",
          "DDMSDatasets": [
            "eml:///dataspace('maap/drogon_dg')/resqml22.TableRepresentation('Drogon-DG2-ProductionForecast')"
